	     <tr><td id=headerrow colspan=2 class=mform valign=top><a name=>&nbsp;</a><a id=sj href=>Class or Race related? Or Bugged?</a> <a id=fs8 href=#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a>
	     <br clear=all><small>Posted @ Mon, Feb 10th 8:55 AM 2003</small></td></tr>
	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=68741><span id=Scholar>The Glorious wordgoddess</span></a><br><b><span id=Scholar>Scholar</span></b><br><span id=notbold>109 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.01]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Hi, all. <br><br>I have a Barb Shaman (finally 30!) and have noticed something lately that made me wonder if my character might not be bugged. <br>I've been playing with my Dwarf Pally (spouse's char) friend and while his mana and health seem to pump up really quickly, mine seem to drag on forever. I knew going in that I wouldn't heal so quickly...and I noticed that earlier in my leveling. However, with Regen, it seems to go a bit better. My problem is that my mana seems to take ages...way more than my health. My spouse thinks it takes freakishly long and I had been thinking the same. At first I thought he might just be used to his char and maybe mine was just a lot slower...but the same situation is happening with our leveling. He's almost 33 (34?) now and while we have been killing mostly greens and light blues (with the occasional dark blue) to his char (they are generally white, dark blue and sometimes light blue to me), he seems to be moving steadily along with leveling while my xp bar barely moves for even whites and yellows. The two things combined make me wonder if this char (my first started) is somehow bugged. <br>Or is it just normal for a Barb Shaman to level so slowly? I thought maybe it was just my half breed class..but he's a pally, so wouldn't it be the same thing? Sheesh. I know I'm rambling, but this has me freaked out (okay, not like that, but &quot;in a tizzy&quot; sounds too weird). <br>Before I posted this, I just saw a post that said Ogres get 10% penalty and Barbs get 5%...could that be it? Might that be the whole problem and it just seems worse? Do any other races have penalties?<br><br>Thanks for any help/input. <br>WG</p>&nbsp;<br></td></td></tr>
